	(2465,546,'went_well','<ul>\r\n 	<li>You are easy on the ear and always looked happy to be representing BCL Solicitors. We discussed the importance of this; people are more likely to listen to you and believe what you say if you are upbeat and engaged with the process of what is going on - even more so when you are saying it with a great voice.</li>\r\n 	<li>You make a strong case for defendants to have representation and used insightful terms to take the listeners/viewers inside the court room. If you speak in the language of the audience, rather than that of lawyers, producers will ask you to come back on a programme and this positions BCL Solicitors as a firm with concern for justice for all, not just its clients.</li>\r\n 	<li>The matters that you raised about polygraphs were interesting; we suggested an observation, such as we are concerned about turning British justice into a Jeremy Kyle show to firmly illustrate your point that I dont know if theyre reliable.</li>\r\n 	<li>You were particularly impressive in arresting the attempt by Kay Burley to you get you to judge the commitment of the government to its initiatives on The Domestic Abuse Bill. By elegantly insisting on referring back to the first question regarding cross-examination, you powerfully, but quietly, re-seized control.\r\n\r\n<strong>Myddleton</strong>: Ellen, you responded well to the sensational approach of the journalist who said that victims of domestic abuse could no longer be cross-examined, by correcting the journalist and saying they could no longer be cross-examined by abusers, but by lawyers.</li>\r\n 	<li>You did well to compress your call for justice for all into a useful sound-bite for BBC News. The third take would enable the producer to use your quote in a clip within a package without having to use the reporters question. Using this technique will ensure that you are quoted and that your messages reach the headlines in-tact.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;'),
	(2464,546,'_overview','field_5b1023299fc62'),
	(2250,515,'_activities_8_activity_name','field_5b11097814d45'),
