	(2862,571,'_activities_4_activity_name','field_5b11097814d45'),
	(2863,571,'activities_4_activity_description','In the final phase we will do a series of video interviews from the perspective of CNBC. The formats will be a pre-recorded clip and a live down the line with the idea being to give Hugues a sense of the different demands of TV and video, so he can adjust his delivery style accordingly.\r\n\r\nIn terms of topics, we will take the best messaging to have emerged up to this point and make that the basis of the interviews to reduce preparation time and allow Hugues to focus on his body language and voice.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),
