	(3035,575,'activities_5_activity_description','Ian is highly supportive of business but dislikes both over-zealous regulators and scoundrels and Kay Burley is a peoples champion who is known to give both corporates and individuals, and the lawyers representing them, a hard time.\r\n\r\nThese are live studio interviews'),
