	(4375,619,'activities_0_activity_description','This will be a short discussion with Hugues about the WSJ interview now the dust has settled and then potentially a talk-through of what will happen at the MWC at the end of February e.g. timings for any confirmed interviews and of course the evolving Huawei story.'),
